POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/management/connections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Organization-Id: {{organizationId}}

{
    "configName": "postgres_no_product",
    "type": "POSTGRESQL",
    "host": "localhost",
    "port": 5432,
    "databaseName": "testdb",
    "userName": "testuser",
    "password": "testpassword"
}

###

### Create Connection - Invalid Host (for testing error handling)
# @name createConnectionInvalidHost
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/management/connections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Organization-Id: {{organizationId}}
X-Product-Name: reporter

{
    "configName": "postgres_invalid",
